videos.headline: Rutgers' Hilliman picks up 32-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Jonathan Hilliman navigates through the Cincinnati defense to score Rutgers' first touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: Illinois recovers fumbled snap for TD
videos.description: AJ Bush Jr. recovers a bobbled snap and runs it in for Illinois' first touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: Bush Jr. runs 41 yards for Illinois TD
videos.description: AJ Bush Jr. navigates through the Rutgers defense to pick up his second touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: Corbin takes off 73 yards for Illini TD
videos.description: Reggie Corbin takes the handoff and bolts 73 yards for another Illinois touchdown.

videos.headline: Rutgers QB Sitkowski finds Vokolek for TD
videos.description: Artur Sitkowski finds a leaping Travis Vokolek with a 7-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Epstein runs 41 yards for Illini TD
videos.description: Mike Epstein finds daylight at the line and jets 41 yards for the touchdown to put Illinois up 38-17.
